## Products API

### Create Product
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Laptop",
  "description": "High-performance laptop",
  "price": 999.99,
  "stockQuantity": 50,
  "category": "Electronics"
}

### Get All Products
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products?page=0&size=10

### Get Product by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/1

### Search Products
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/search?query=laptop

### Filter Products
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/filter?category=Electronics&minPrice=100&maxPrice=2000

### Update Product
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Laptop Pro",
  "description": "High-performance laptop with extended warranty",
  "price": 1099.99,
  "stockQuantity": 45,
  "category": "Electronics"
}

### Delete Product
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/products/1

---

## Orders API

### Create Order
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "productIds": [1, 2, 3]
}

### Get All Orders
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders?page=0&size=10

### Get Order by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1

### Get Orders by User
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/user/1

### Filter Orders
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/filter?userId=1&status=PENDING

### Update Order Status
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1/status?status=PROCESSING

### Delete Order
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1

